These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, lacrosse, snowboarding, water-polo
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, drawing, baking, fishing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, western, romance, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, horse, rat
 1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 7. the person watching western movies is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 8. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the rat and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
10. the person who's sport is sailing is the owner of the rat##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Sport          | snowboarding  | sailing    | water-polo    | lacrosse   |
| Hobby   | drawing     | video-games   | baking       | fishing    |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | time-travel    | romance |
| Pet           | hamster | rat       | chinchilla | horse     |

