.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, grey, pink, aquamarine
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, drawing, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, gospel, rock, funk
House: futuristic, art-deco, palace, colonial
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
 2. the fan of gospel is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 4. the person who likes grey is the fan of country##1
 5. the colonial house is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 6. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
 7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 8. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
 9. the fan of rock is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who likes pink is in an odd position##4
11. the fan of rock is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Color          | chestnut  | grey    | pink     | aquamarine       |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | baking   | collecting |
| Music-Genre   | rock | country   | gospel   | funk    |
| House         | palace | colonial  | futuristic | art-deco   |

