.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda, sprite
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, subway, bike, boat
4 different games are played: snooker, monopoly, domino, go
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, blues, salsa, techno
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 2. the person playing monopoly is the person driving the bike##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 5. the person drinking juice is the person driving the boat##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 7. the fan of jazz is the person playing go##1
 8. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
10. the fan of jazz is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | sprite    | juice      |
| Transport           | bike | bus | subway | boat     |
| Game   | monopoly      | go   | snooker   | domino |
| Music-Genre           | techno         | jazz       | salsa  | blues       |

