.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
House: ranch-style, tower, colonial, palace
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, soul, rock, blues
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, dunhill, davidoff, dannemann
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, parkour, surfing
 1. the ranch-style house is the fan of electronic##1
 2. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 3. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 4. the dunhill-smoker is in an even position##4
 5. the tower house is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 7. the palace house is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is the dunhill-smoker##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
11. the colonial house is the fan of blues##1
12. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| House   | palace       | colonial   | ranch-style   | tower   |
| Music-Genre       | soul        | blues | electronic    | rock       |
| Cigar      | dannemann | dunhill    | davidoff  | old-henry |
| Sport      | ice-hockey  | parkour  | cycling | surfing    |

