.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, orange, pineapple, spinach
House: cape-cod, ranch-style, gothic-revival, townhouse
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, dahlia, iris, sunflower
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, almond-milk, soy-milk
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the gothic-revival house is between the person drinking sprite and the person eating spinach##2
 3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 4. the person who growsdahlia is the person eating kiwi##1
 5. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
 6. the cape-cod house is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating orange is the person who growsorchid##1
 8. the gothic-revival house is the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the townhouse house##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
12. the townhouse house is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | pineapple    | spinach      | kiwi          | orange    |
| House   | ranch-style | townhouse       | gothic-revival | cape-cod |
| Flower     | sunflower     | iris      | dahlia     | orchid |
| Beverage   | coffee   | soy-milk | almond-milk        | sprite   |

