 9. the owner of the dog is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who likes lavender##2
10. the designer is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
11. the scientist is in an even position##4
12. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the chef##3

.:: Answer ::.
