The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, house, indie, jazz
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, backgammon, whist
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of folk is between the person traveling to prague and the person playing scrabble##2
 4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 5. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 6. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 7. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing whist is the person traveling to prague##1
 9. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
11. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of house is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
13. the fan of indie is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Pet          | fish     | cat      | hedgehog  | hamster        |
| City   | prague     | rome | london | miami      |
| Music-Genre   | house      | folk        | jazz        | indie        |
| Game         | whist | mah-jongg    | scrabble      | backgammon |

