.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, juice, milk
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, lilac, lavender, amber
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, may, july
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, electrician, coach, designer
 1. the electrician is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 2. the designer is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4
 5. the police-officer is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 7. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
10. the coach is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
12. the person who likes blue is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice       | hot-chocolate | 7up        | milk        |
| Color         | amber | lavender       | blue | lilac |
| Birthday   | july     | september        | august    | may      |
| Job         | electrician     | coach    | designer | police-officer   |

