.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, blend, swisher, alhambra
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, french, indonesian, polish
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, architect, fisherman, project-manager
4 different games are played: go, monopoly, domino, bridge
 1. the alhambra-smoker is the fisherman##1
 2. the fisherman is between the australian and the polish##2
 3. the fisherman is on the left or right of the doctor##3
 4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the french##1
 5. the doctor is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 6. the blend-smoker is the architect##1
 7. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
 8. the polish is in an even position##4
 9. the architect is on the left or right of the doctor##3
10. the australian is in an even position##4
11. the australian is on the far right##1
12. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar   | blend      | montecristo | alhambra     | swisher        |
| Nationality   | indonesian | polish  | french     | australian |
| Job         | architect    | doctor | fisherman      | project-manager |
| Game     | bridge | monopoly     | domino | go       |

 